Sarah was an ordinary everyday gal until a radioactive spider...
Wait a minute, that's not right. I think I was working in a lab when lighting struck, splashing chemicals all over me, giving me...
Wait, wait, wait. That's not right either, and it's crossing two different publishers. What's in it for me to tell you my origin story, huh?


I work in a comic shop, and I specialize in stealing trash cans.
